<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="amount-n">amount <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'maʊnt/    美 /ə'maʊnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 数量；数额；总数：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When you are traveling, don’t display <strong>large amounts of</strong> cash to others.
旅行时，不要向他人显露大量的现金。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A little bit of kindness will be rewarded with <strong>a huge amount of</strong> benefits.
滴水之恩当涌泉相报。</p></div>

<p>注: amounts of / a large (huge / small) amount of 尤与不可数名词连用。作主语时，谓语动词的单复数与amount的数保持一致。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Large amounts of money were spent on building the bridge. 
大量的资金用在了这座桥的建造上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There’s only a small amount of food. 
只有一点儿食物。</p></div></div>